I '''Leo Tolstoy''', o kaya Conti '''Lev Nikolayevich Tolstoy''' ({{audio-ru|Лев Никола́евич Толсто́й|Ru-Lev Nikolayevich Tolstoy.ogg}}, {{IPA-ru|lʲɛv nʲɪkɐˈlaɪvʲɪtɕ tɐlˈstoj}}; {{OldStyleDate|September 9|1828|August 28}} – {{OldStyleDate|November 20|1910|November 7}}), metung yang Russian talasulat maleparan a makikilala bilang metung kareng pekamatenakan a novelista. Ding kayang obra maestra ilapin deng ''[[Guerra ampong Kapayapan (War and Peace)]]'' ampong ''[[Anna Karenina]]'' ila deng maglarawan keng lalam, lapad, ampong mabieng papakit ing pang19 dilanuang (siglu) bie king [[Russia]] ampong panlalawe, ing taluktuk ning [[realism (arts)|realist fiction]].{{Citation needed|date=November 2009}}.



